snippet.title: DON'T EVEN THINK - Official Open Beta Launch Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
To be or not to be, you will not have time to think about this.
DON'T EVEN THINK(Open Beta) launches now! 
Free download on the PlayStation® Store (Hong Kong). 
The fast-paced battle royale of 8 players is firstly availble to play. A whole new world is waiting for you to conquer!
